        "content": "<p>Our award-winning JS Party game show is back with a new name, a new channel, and the same ol' survey-response-guessing fun! The JS Party crew join us to see who knows y'all best. Survey says! <span aria-label=\"link\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f517\" role=\"img\" title=\"link\">:link:</span> <a href=\"https://changelog.am/83\">https://changelog.am/83</a></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Ch</th>\n<th>Start</th>\n<th>Title</th>\n<th>Runs</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>01</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=0\">00:00</a></td>\n<td>Let's play!</td>\n<td>00:38</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>02</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=38\">00:38</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.augmentcode.com\">Sponsor: Augment Code</a></td>\n<td>03:09</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>03</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=226\">03:46</a></td>\n<td>Feuding &amp; Friends</td>\n<td>03:55</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>04</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=462\">07:42</a></td>\n<td>Game rules</td>\n<td>03:03</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>05</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=644\">10:44</a></td>\n<td>Round 1: Name a robot</td>\n<td>06:25</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>06</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=1029\">17:09</a></td>\n<td>Round 2: Favorite file format</td>\n<td>08:10</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>07</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=1519\">25:19</a></td>\n<td>Round 3: Least favorite file format</td>\n<td>08:43</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>08</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=2043\">34:03</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://retool.com/changelog\">Sponsor: Retool</a></td>\n<td>02:57</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>09</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=2220\">37:00</a></td>\n<td>Round 4: First protocol</td>\n<td>06:27</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=2607\">43:27</a></td>\n<td>Round 5: 1 &lt;= N &lt;= 20</td>\n<td>07:09</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=3035\">50:35</a></td>\n<td>Round 6: 1 &lt;= N &lt;= 20 meta</td>\n<td>04:44</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>12</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=3319\">55:19</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://temporal.io\">Sponsor: Temporal</a></td>\n<td>02:21</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=3461\">57:41</a></td>\n<td>Round 7: Programming-related movie</td>\n<td>04:01</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>14</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=3702\">1:01:42</a></td>\n<td>And the winner is...</td>\n<td>02:26</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>15</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=3847\">1:04:07</a></td>\n<td>The winner's circle</td>\n<td>01:18</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>16</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=3926\">1:05:26</a></td>\n<td>Showing our age</td>\n<td>05:31</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=4256\">1:10:56</a></td>\n<td>Bye, friends</td>\n<td>00:29</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>18</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.am/83#t=4285\">1:11:25</a></td>\n<td>Coming up next</td>\n<td>01:08</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
